In patients with unprovoked VTE, does the addition of FDG PET/CT to a limited 
occult cancer screening strategy offer good value for money? A 
cost-effectiveness analysis from the publicly funded health care systems.

Robin P(1), Kumar S(2), Salaun PY(3), Le Roux PY(4), Couturaud F(5), Planquette 
