Clinical classification of cervical necrotizing fasciitis.

Amponsah EK(1), Frimpong P(1), Eo MY(2), Kim SM(3)(4), Lee SK(5).

Author information:
(1)Oral and Maxillofacial Microvascular Reconstruction Lab, Ghana Health 
Service, Brong Ahafo Regional Hospital, P. O. Box 27, Sunyani, Brong Ahafo, 
Ghana.
(2)Department of Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery, Dental Research Institute, 
School of Dentistry, Seoul National University, Seoul, South Korea.
(3)Oral and Maxillofacial Microvascular Reconstruction Lab, Ghana Health 
Service, Brong Ahafo Regional Hospital, P. O. Box 27, Sunyani, Brong Ahafo, 
Ghana. smin5@snu.ac.kr.
(4)Department of Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery, Dental Research Institute, 
